**contract** (goal + acceptance criteria) is at the top — workers read it to
learn what "done" means. The **progress** section below tracks waves and
verified criteria and is re-written on every change (plan approve, checker
verdict, wave completion). Do not redefine the criteria here — propose
changes through the plan.

